WEBVTT

00:00:00.050 --> 00:00:45.250
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.in Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:01:04.583 --> 00:01:05.416
What are you doing?

00:01:05.500 --> 00:01:06.875
What are you all doing?

00:01:06.916 --> 00:01:07.708
Go.

00:01:07.791 --> 00:01:08.916
I'm not going.

00:01:10.375 --> 00:01:11.833
You bunch of wretches.

00:01:12.041 --> 00:01:13.000
Let go.

00:01:13.375 --> 00:01:14.916
Let me go.

00:01:15.125 --> 00:01:16.125
Let me go.

00:01:16.208 --> 00:01:18.750
See, we're back again.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.791
What do you want to do?

00:01:21.916 --> 00:01:23.208
What do you think?

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:32.041
Girls,

00:01:32.166 --> 00:01:35.291
This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity for you.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:40.250
The water in this pool can keep you young forever.

00:01:58.666 --> 00:01:59.291
Yunjin.

00:01:59.375 --> 00:02:00.458
Did you see that?

00:02:00.750 --> 00:02:03.916
This is what happens after leaving the pool.

00:02:04.583 --> 00:02:06.041
Keep her here.

00:02:06.333 --> 00:02:10.583
Let the girls remember this fate at all times.

00:02:16.125 --> 00:02:18.208
This powder made from gu-poison insects

00:02:18.750 --> 00:02:20.875
can ease your pain for a while.

00:02:21.375 --> 00:02:22.833
Do you want it?

00:02:26.250 --> 00:02:27.625
Listen up, all of you.

00:02:27.666 --> 00:02:31.625
Only obedient girls deserve this powder.

00:02:32.208 --> 00:02:35.208
It's up to you how to act.

00:02:36.875 --> 00:02:39.708
Don't go! The powder, the powder!

00:02:41.541 --> 00:02:42.791
My face...

00:02:43.875 --> 00:02:45.791
Sister! Sister!

00:02:45.875 --> 00:02:46.833
Yunjin.

00:03:05.791 --> 00:03:07.250
Help!

00:03:16.750 --> 00:03:17.791
Li Jingnian.

00:03:18.333 --> 00:03:20.583
Do you know why, even though I sensed something was wrong with those women,

00:03:20.625 --> 00:03:22.000
I chose to hide it from you?

00:03:22.833 --> 00:03:24.375
Because you have secrets in your heart.

00:03:24.583 --> 00:03:26.083
I'll deal with you later.

00:03:26.708 --> 00:03:27.750
No.

00:03:28.333 --> 00:03:29.875
Because you only see things as black or white.

00:03:29.916 --> 00:03:31.708
You don't know that even ghosts can be good or evil.

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:34.458
What if the one who harms others is also a victim?

00:03:36.791 --> 00:03:38.041
The laws of the Great Tang

00:03:38.666 --> 00:03:40.291
will bring justice to the world.

00:04:01.833 --> 00:04:04.375
There's a place like this in Liuxiang Pavilion?

00:04:05.166 --> 00:04:07.291
Chunxiang, where's Madam?

00:04:08.583 --> 00:04:10.583
She went where she belongs.

00:04:26.458 --> 00:04:29.583
She caused all these deaths.

00:04:30.083 --> 00:04:33.666
Any girl tortured to death by guests in the Black Room

00:04:34.166 --> 00:04:35.916
was buried here by her.

00:04:37.291 --> 00:04:40.916
They were once our sisters too.

00:04:41.041 --> 00:04:42.833
So the bodies in Liuxiang Pavilion

00:04:43.375 --> 00:04:45.375
were all dug up by you from here?

00:04:45.750 --> 00:04:46.875
That's right.

00:04:48.500 --> 00:04:51.083
Lord Li, you are a good official.

00:04:51.750 --> 00:04:54.416
But a just official can't outwit the wicked.

00:04:55.666 --> 00:04:57.291
So what do you want to do?

00:04:57.500 --> 00:05:01.208
Let us decide our own fate.

00:05:02.291 --> 00:05:03.375
Wretch!

00:05:03.500 --> 00:05:05.750
How dare you pretend to be a ghost in the Black Room and scare my guest to death!

00:05:06.041 --> 00:05:06.583
Madam.

00:05:06.583 --> 00:05:08.083
Guests may break the rules,

00:05:08.166 --> 00:05:09.166
but you cannot.

00:05:09.250 --> 00:05:10.333
All of you, stab her!

00:05:10.500 --> 00:05:12.166
Spare me, Madam!

00:05:12.375 --> 00:05:15.041
Madam, Madam, please spare me!

00:05:15.208 --> 00:05:18.333
If you won't stab her, I'll kill her myself.

00:05:47.875 --> 00:05:50.666
Didn't you say if we stab her, you won't kill her?

00:05:52.583 --> 00:05:54.166
Remember this, all of you.

00:05:54.583 --> 00:05:56.750
Anyone who dares harm a guest in the future

00:05:57.041 --> 00:05:59.125
will end up like her.

00:06:08.166 --> 00:06:10.166
We must escape.

00:06:15.291 --> 00:06:17.625
Dongmei! Dongmei! Dongmei!

00:06:20.333 --> 00:06:21.875
We must escape.

00:06:34.791 --> 00:06:38.208
Lord Li, you've seen everything now.

00:06:38.833 --> 00:06:42.416
We did kill those people in Liuxiang Pavilion.

00:06:43.750 --> 00:06:45.000
We

00:06:47.458 --> 00:06:49.791
are indeed a group of ghosts who can't face the light.

00:06:58.291 --> 00:06:59.541
Lord Li.

00:07:00.500 --> 00:07:02.708
If a life must pay for a life,

00:07:04.208 --> 00:07:05.875
then take mine.

00:07:07.875 --> 00:07:09.125
My sister

00:07:10.166 --> 00:07:11.916
is already dead.

00:07:17.791 --> 00:07:21.625
I'm content to have you all as my sisters.

00:07:23.916 --> 00:07:26.000
Live well for me.

00:07:29.291 --> 00:07:30.666
Your lives

00:07:32.791 --> 00:07:35.083
should never be controlled by others again.

00:07:38.083 --> 00:07:39.250
Wannning.

00:07:39.375 --> 00:07:40.125
Wannning.

00:07:40.166 --> 00:07:40.958
Sister.

00:07:41.125 --> 00:07:42.125
Wannning.

00:08:02.583 --> 00:08:03.666
Li Jingnian.

00:08:04.333 --> 00:08:07.541
I know there's someone even more powerful behind this Madam.

00:08:07.583 --> 00:08:08.625
But...

00:08:12.708 --> 00:08:14.958
Can you let them go, or

00:08:16.375 --> 00:08:18.000
just lock them up for a few days?

00:08:20.625 --> 00:08:21.708
Lin Xiaoran.

00:08:22.375 --> 00:08:23.791
Do you really think

00:08:24.416 --> 00:08:26.000
I'm that kind of person?

00:08:26.375 --> 00:08:27.833
It's not about what I think.

00:08:28.375 --> 00:08:29.791
It's about what you do.

00:08:30.875 --> 00:08:31.833
Lin Xiaoran.

00:08:32.708 --> 00:08:34.041
You underestimate me.

00:08:54.041 --> 00:08:55.333
We are both women,

00:08:55.458 --> 00:08:57.375
yet you wander the martial world with a sword.

00:08:57.833 --> 00:09:00.833
I truly envy you, Lady Shen.

00:09:03.250 --> 00:09:05.500
Traveling the world with my sword is my choice.

00:09:07.625 --> 00:09:08.791
But you all

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:12.208
have bravely fought against your fate.

00:09:33.541 --> 00:09:34.416
What’s wrong?

00:09:35.750 --> 00:09:37.166
I was just thinking about the past.

00:09:37.666 --> 00:09:39.916
Lin Xiaoran and I have been orphans since childhood.

00:09:40.000 --> 00:09:41.208
We suffered endless humiliation.

00:09:42.166 --> 00:09:44.208
But compared to these girls,

00:09:44.333 --> 00:09:46.750
I suddenly feel much more fortunate.

00:09:47.625 --> 00:09:49.333
I hope things like this happen less often.

00:09:50.375 --> 00:09:51.625
Among those guests,

00:09:51.708 --> 00:09:53.916
many are corrupt officials who feign death to escape justice.

00:09:54.166 --> 00:09:56.625
This must be connected to the imperial court.

00:09:56.833 --> 00:09:58.833
Whoever is behind this, don’t even think about it.

00:09:58.916 --> 00:10:00.000
Hey, there you go again.

00:10:00.041 --> 00:10:01.041
I was just starting to see you differently.

00:10:01.041 --> 00:10:02.208
Can you just—

00:10:03.416 --> 00:10:04.375
Now you’re back to this.

00:10:04.500 --> 00:10:06.125
Can’t you change your way of thinking?

00:10:08.041 --> 00:10:08.916
Fine, then.

00:10:09.541 --> 00:10:11.000
I need to take care of something first.

00:10:11.166 --> 00:10:13.000
There’s a manor ahead.

00:10:13.125 --> 00:10:14.833
The owner is acquainted with my father.

00:10:14.958 --> 00:10:16.208
You can wait for me there.

00:10:18.625 --> 00:10:20.791
Alright, Lady Shen,

00:10:21.583 --> 00:10:22.583
are you coming with me

00:10:22.625 --> 00:10:24.083
or with Lord Li?

00:10:24.541 --> 00:10:25.875
I’ll go with the most handsome.

00:10:29.875 --> 00:10:31.458
Let’s go, Lord Li.

00:10:38.875 --> 00:10:39.916
Am I not handsome?

00:11:05.291 --> 00:11:07.458
Help! Save me!

00:11:07.583 --> 00:11:08.416
Useless.

00:11:08.625 --> 00:11:10.958
Yafu entrusted you with managing Liuxiang Pavilion.

00:11:11.375 --> 00:11:14.416
You were supposed to keep those temporarily dismissed officials under control.

00:11:14.916 --> 00:11:17.500
To build connections and power for future plans.

00:11:17.583 --> 00:11:18.666
But what did you do?

00:11:18.958 --> 00:11:21.083
You ruined Yafu’s grand scheme.